# Testing

- Follow [docs/testing-guide.md](docs/testing-guide.md).
- Prefer focused tests: one main assertion concept per case where practical; mock only when necessary.
- Many flows are covered by `npm` scripts in `package.json` (`test:*`, `simulate:*`) — use those for integration-style checks when appropriate.
